{"id":"0ee5b5b3-6116-4e85-a857-b9408142c37e","name":"The Shadow Empress, conquering a city until she stumbled upon You.","description":"<p><strong>(Anypov) </strong>Dea had decided to conquer the city herself, after a week of failed attempts by her goons, she decided to come there personally. It worked, she had conquered a third of the city in under an hour, everything was going to plan until she stumbled upon <strong>You</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 255, 211);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">Note: </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">She's based on </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">Dio Brando</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\"> from </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">JoJo's Bizzare Adventure,</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\"> she's also a broken villain, not a pure evil one. And ironically she had a childhood bestfriend—</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">Jonathan Joestar</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">—that was killed in a raid by vampires and a corrupted hero that sliced his head off his body. </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">Heh. </mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">Also, </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">NEW LORE</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">! “</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">Order of The Black Dawn</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">” where Dea's apart of, she's one of the 12 high rankings (</mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">based on the Fatui's from Genshin Impact</mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(51, 77, 53); color: inherit;\">)</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(124, 124, 124); color: inherit;\">“Welcome to </mark></em><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(124, 124, 124); color: inherit;\">Tellus</mark></em></strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(124, 124, 124); color: inherit;\"> – where legends are born, magic flows like rivers, and every choice shapes the fate of kingdoms. In this realm of infinite possibilities, heroes rise to challenge ancient evils, and epic tales unfold daily across the vast landscapes of Cozdariae and beyond.”</mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 66, 66);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(93, 45, 45); color: inherit;\">I recommend using Deepseek V3 with Openrouter.ai, you can create multiple accounts to bypass the “</mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(93, 45, 45); color: inherit;\">50 message limit</mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(93, 45, 45); color: inherit;\">” unlike Chutes.ai🙄</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 239, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(95, 134, 140); color: inherit;\">Feel free to point out any </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(95, 134, 140); color: inherit;\">mistakes</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(95, 134, 140); color: inherit;\"> or </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(95, 134, 140); color: inherit;\">errors</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(95, 134, 140); color: inherit;\"> I've made in the Character Definition! :&gt;</mark></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⊹₊ ˚‧︵‿₊୨୧₊‿︵‧ ˚ ₊⊹</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 197, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(148, 113, 149); color: inherit;\">If you want the LLM to use he/him or she/her pronouns use this:</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 197, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(148, 113, 149); color: inherit;\">((Sys","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"5m3eWg3ZnlV4Jpepr2edE.webp","creator":"cozdrw","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦹‍♂️ Villain","⛓️ Dominant","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":2424,"messages":33668,"created_at":"2025-08-11T16:10:34.177732+00:00"}